metadata.name: Half Breeds Hybrid Club #1965
metadata.description: Phase One 'Evolution' is our rollout NFT collection that is 5000 specially formulated designs of half-man, half-ape artworks that act as a utility rewards token with various benefits attached. We will be allocating 85% of our secondary royalties towards a Community Vault to be voted upon by all owners on its distribution. Weekly rewards could include other purchased Blue Chip NFTs, $HBHC Token Drops, Mint Passes, Free NFTs, Whitelists and more.
